        "item_tVpzTf": {
          "type": "item",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "icon_width": 20,
            "title": "SPECIFICATION",
            "content": "<p>REAR BRAKE: Yes<br/><br/>SEAT BELT: 5-point equipped with magnetic buckle<br/><br/>BASKET WITH COVER: Yes<br/><br/>FOOTRESTS: Basic (foldable) + accessory portable<br/>(for infants)<br/><br/>PARENT RIDE CONTROL HANDLEBAR: Height adjustable, two-position<br/><br/>WHEEL DIAMETER:<br/>12 inches (front wheel)<br/>10 inches (rear wheels)<br/><br/>ADJUSTABLE BACK SUPPORT:<br/>Two-position<br/><br/>FREE HANDLE BAR FUNCTION:Yes<br/><br/>STORAGE BAG: Compact, removable<br/><br/>SEAT COVER: Removable and machine washable<br/><br/>HEADRES: Yielding soft headrest with stitched Bentley<br/>badge<br/><br/>WHEEL FENDERS: Yes<br/><br/>USED MATERIALS:<br/>Iron, PVC, PP, ABC, TPR<br/><br/>FOLDABLE CANOPY: Two-position<br/>FREEWHEEL FUNCTION: Yes<br/><br/>SEAT ROTATING FUNCTION: 180 grees</p>",
            "page": "bentley-trike-assembly"
          }
        },
        "item_QMVwhR": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "icon_width": 20,
            "title": "HOW TO ASSEMBLE",
            "content": "<p>Every tool you need to put together your new Bentley Trike comes neatly organized in your box. Simply follow  <a href=\"https://bentleytrike.com/pages/bentley-trike-assembly\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://bentleytrike.com/pages/bentley-trike-assembly\">these simple steps</a>.<br/><br/>To help you even further, we’ve added more resources:<br/><br/><a href=\"https://bentleytrike.com/pages/bentley-trike-instructional-videos\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://bentleytrike.com/pages/bentley-trike-instructional-videos\">Bentley Trike Instructional Videos <br/><br/></a><a href=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0008/3368/3521/files/Bentley_trike_Manual_Print_compressed.pdf?v=1764271651\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0008/3368/3521/files/Bentley_trike_Manual_Print_compressed.pdf?v=1764271651\">Downloadable Assembly Manual (PDF)</a></p>",
            "page": "bentley-trike-assembly"
          }
        },
        "item_LLNwn9": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "icon_width": 20,
            "title": "SPARE PARTS",
            "content": "<p>Every journey deserves to be seamless. If any part of your Bentley Trike needs replacing, continue the experience by ordering an official Bentley spare part <a href=\"/products/bentley-trike-spare-parts\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Bentley Trike Spare Parts\">here</a>. </p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "item_H639BW": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "icon_width": 20,
            "title": "WARRANTY",
            "content": "<p>If you experience any issues with your Bentley Trike within the <strong>2-year warranty </strong>period, we’re here to ensure a seamless solution. Simply enter your details in the form below, and our team will assist you promptly.</p><p><em>Please note : Warranty coverage applies exclusively to purchases made directly from us. If purchased elsewhere, kindly reach out to the original retailer for assistance</em></p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        }
