            "title": "The Bentley Badge",
            "text": "<p>The trike’s chrome emblem is a tribute to the iconic Bentley badge found on the <strong>Continental GT Mulliner</strong>—a symbol of prestige and craftsmanship. <br/><br/>More than just a detail, it reflects our dedication to luxury and perfection in every ride.</p>",
